          },
          {
            "id": "S06_stage_zh",
            "lang": "zh",
            "text": "阳光和小雨\n暖暖阳光，轻轻小雨",
            "font_size_pt": 21,
            "visible_in": [
              "stage",
              "rehearsal"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "speaker": {
        "script_en": "Pinky also needs sunshine and gentle rain. Sunshine makes her warm. Rain makes the soil soft. Together, they help her grow stronger.",
        "script_zh": "小粉还需要阳光和温柔的小雨。阳光让她暖暖的，小雨让泥土变软。它们一起帮助她长得更结实。",
        "actions": [
          "open both hands"
        ]
      },
