            "id": "S07_stage_zh",
            "lang": "zh",
            "text": "我慢慢等。\n长大需要时间",
            "font_size_pt": 21,
            "visible_in": [
              "stage",
              "rehearsal"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "speaker": {
        "script_en": "Some days, nothing big happens. I only see the same little bud. But I wait. I know growing takes time and patience.",
        "script_zh": "有些日子，看起来没有发生很大的变化。我只看到同一个小花苞。但是我会等，因为长大需要时间和耐心。",
