            "lang": "zh",
            "text": "有一天下午……\n花苞打开了！",
            "font_size_pt": 21,
            "visible_in": [
              "stage",
              "rehearsal"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "speaker": {
        "script_en": "One afternoon, I saw something beautiful. Pinky’s bud opened like a small pink umbrella. I was surprised, and I called my mom.",
        "script_zh": "有一天下午，我看见了很美的事情。小粉的花苞打开了，像一把粉色的小伞。我很惊喜，马上叫妈妈来看。",
        "actions": [
          "look surprised"
        ]
      },
