            "text": "What I learned\nlove, water, sunshine, time",
            "font_size_pt": 25,
            "visible_in": [
              "stage",
              "rehearsal"
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "S10_stage_zh",
            "lang": "zh",
            "text": "我学到了什么\n爱，水，阳光，时间",
            "font_size_pt": 21,
            "visible_in": [
              "stage",
              "rehearsal"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "speaker": {
        "script_en": "My little flower taught me this. Small things can grow with love, water, sunshine, and time. Even a tiny bud can become bright.",
        "script_zh": "我的小花教会了我一件事：小小的东西，也可以在爱、水、阳光和时间里慢慢长大。小小的花苞，也能变得很明亮。",
        "actions": [
          "show flower with hands"
        ]
      },
